a2t.text_actual: Create & join Club with new friends around you! Finding friends become so much fun and exciting. Want to ride bicycle or go see a movie together? Just check out Club now! Club Create & Join clubs around you. Meet new Friends with the same Interests. Look Around Discover people within close distance from you. 50m? 100m? 1km?  Find Friends from nearby! Radar Scan the area and Find even more new Friends! Whisper Send messages that magically disappear after being read! Free Calls and Messages Unlimited talk time, texts and voice messages Doodle Sketch and draw to your friends! Stickers Enrich your chatting experience with cute stickers! Group Chat Group Vote allows us to find out others' preferences
